squished friends...) but that's the way it's done by rock-crawlers, and
nobody usually gets squished...

BTW, My '71 has gotten me through more miles of nasty, insane roads than I
can count, and required only minimal and reasonable service in return.  Go
for it, Miles, you've got the right name to go the distance, for sure!

> - Miles ('71 Bus - 700 miles on new Mexican engine, running strong!)

